quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,7,"Ni gute ababangikanyamana bagirana amasezerano na Allah ndetse n’Intumwa ye, batari babandi mwagiranye amasezerano ku Musigiti Mutagatifu (Ka’aba)? Igihe cyose bazabatunganira (bubahiriza amase- zerano), namwe muzaba-tunganire (muyubahirize). Mu by’ukuri, Allah akunda abamutinya"
  9,8,"Ni gute (mwagirana amasezerano nk’ayo nabo) kandi iyo babanesheje batita ku masano cyangwa amasezerano mwagiranye? Babagusha neza mu magambo gusa, nyamara imitima yabo itabyemera, kandi abenshi muri bo ni ibyigomeke"
  9,9,"Baguranye amagambo ya Allah igiciro gito, banakumira (abantu kugana) inzira ye. Mu by’ukuri, ibyo bakoraga ni bibi"
  9,10,(Abo babangikanyamana) ntibu- bahiriza isano cyangwa isezerano bafitanye n’umwemera! Kandi abo ni bo barengera (imbago za Allah)
  9,11,"Nibaramuka bicujije bagahozaho amasengesho, ndetse bakanatanga amaturo, ubwo bazaba babaye abavandimwe banyu mu idini. (Uko ni ko) dusobanura amagambo (yacu) ku bantu bafite ubumenyi"
  9,12,"Ariko nibatatira indahiro zabo nyuma y’amasezerano (mwagiranye) bakanasebya idini ryanyu, mujye murwanya abayobozi b’ubuhakanyi kugira ngo barekeraho (ibikorwa byabo bibi), kuko mu by’ukuri nta sezerano bajya bubahiriza"
  9,13,"Kuki mutarwanya abantu batatiye indahiro zabo bakanashaka kumenesha Intumwa (Muhamadi), kandi ari bo babashotoye bwa mbere? murabatinya? Ahubwo Allah ni we Ese mukwiye gutinya niba koko muri abemera"